The first time he saw her, it was love at first sight. Unfortunately for Sorata Kanda, "she" was a cat named Hikari and his school's rules forbid keeping pets in the regular dorms. As a result, Sorata is banished to the infamous Sakura Hall alongside other troublesome and unusual students like Jin, overzealous playboy, Ryuunosuke, the reclusive hermit, and Mashiro, a brilliant artist who's so unfocused and clueless about the real world that dorm supervisor Ms. Sengoku assigns Sorata the task of taking care of her along with his ever-growing collection of stray cats!
(Source: Sentai Filmworks)
Action, Drama, Horror, Mystery, Psychological, Supernatural

The suspense horror/dark fantasy story is set in Tokyo, which is haunted by mysterious "ghouls" who are devouring humans. People are gripped by the fear of these ghouls whose identities are masked in mystery. An ordinary college student named Kaneki encounters Rize, a girl who is an avid reader like him, at the caf he frequents. Little does he realize that his fate will change overnight.
(Source: Anime News Network)
Monster ga Afureru Sekai ni Natta kedo, Tayoreru Neko ga Iru kara Daijoubu desu.

On her way home from shopping for dinner, Kujo Ayame, a new member of society who lives with her tortoiseshell cat, Haru, gets caught up in the drastic changes in the world. The changed cityscape, monsters attacking people, and people awakening to their skills....
In the turmoil, Ayame and Haru accidentally succeed in defeating a giant monster, and at that moment, a voice echoes in their heads. ["Kujo Ayame's LV has increased from 1 to 10"]
["Confirming the first named monster defeat in Chaos Frontier Acquired the bonus skill "Search"]
With that as a trigger, Ayame made full use of her search skill to survive in a overflowing with monsters.
Moreover, Ayame is not the only one who has awakened to this skill; her cat Haru has also acquired the useful cheat-level skill "Conversion"!
(Source: GA Novels, translated)
Inma Tsuihou: Hentai Gift wo Sazukatta Sei de Outo Owareru mo, Onnanoko to "Nakayoku" suru Dake de Chouzetsu Level Up

A world where one's life is decided by one's talent, called a "Gift." The main character, Erio Scarlet, who was born in the house of an influential noble family that had produced a lot of Holy Knights, manifested a suspicious Gift called "Incubus" in the conferment ceremony. Furthermore, the only skill attached to that Gift was one embarrassingly called "Peerless."
Erio was banished from the city because there was no way his indecent existence could be permitted in a family of Holy Knights, but... somehow he went through an amazing growth when he dealt with his horniness?! In addition, when his childhood friend who was bestowed with the Gift "Sacred Knight" chased after him and reverse ra... did it with him, a lot of powerful indecent skills showed up, and on top of that they even got bound by Master-Servant contract...?!
This is the indecent heroic tale of the boy who was gifted with and indecent Gift rising in the world while "getting along" with a lot of girls.
